          <declname>button_id</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Convenience function to clear out an existing icon. All it does is call <computeroutput>action_bar_layer_set_icon(action_bar, button_id, NULL)</computeroutput> </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
