          <type><ref refid="group___clicks_1gaac872430f49a1bee56078e7b1f4a202a" kindref="member">ClickConfigProvider</ref></type>
          <declname>click_config_provider</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Sets the click configuration provider callback of the action bar. In this callback your application can associate handlers to the different types of click events for each of the buttons, see <ref refid="group___clicks" kindref="compound">Clicks</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>If the action bar had already been added to a window and the window is currently on-screen, the click configuration provider will be called before this function returns. Otherwise, it will be called by the system when the window becomes on-screen. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>The <computeroutput>.raw</computeroutput> handlers cannot be used without breaking the automatic highlighting of the segment of the action bar that for which a button is </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="group___action_bar_layer_1ga03f3cf8b2817e31ff6c9b670f934dfe6" kindref="member">action_bar_layer_set_icon()</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>action_bar</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The action bar for which to assign a new click configuration provider </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>click_config_provider</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The new click configuration provider </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
