<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Initialize<sp/>the<sp/>action<sp/>bar:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>action_bar<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="group___action_bar_layer_1ga8070ea0e56c090655c5cf0697ee22831" kindref="member">action_bar_layer_create</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Associate<sp/>the<sp/>action<sp/>bar<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>window:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
