<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>click_config_provider);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Set<sp/>the<sp/>icons:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>The<sp/>loading<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>icons<sp/>is<sp/>omitted<sp/>for<sp/>brevity...<sp/>See<sp/>gbitmap_create_with_resource()</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><ref refid="group___action_bar_layer_1gafb562eb59d855d5e3a394b6b28195727" kindref="member">action_bar_layer_set_icon_animated</ref>(action_bar,<sp/><ref refid="group___clicks_1ggaa60e15d86cfe7033f28c7d066c85266eafb03cb7921a8bb7893cd8093a1a5e9cb" kindref="member">BUTTON_ID_UP</ref>,<sp/>my_icon_previous,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">true</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><ref refid="group___action_bar_layer_1gafb562eb59d855d5e3a394b6b28195727" kindref="member">action_bar_layer_set_icon_animated</ref>(action_bar,<sp/><ref refid="group___clicks_1ggaa60e15d86cfe7033f28c7d066c85266ea65a919b8a0f4539acfb865eb2a2dd9d0" kindref="member">BUTTON_ID_DOWN</ref>,<sp/>my_icon_next,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">true</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
